Nairobi based Revitalize Wellness Center has been ranked the best luxury spa and wellness center in Africa at the Luxury Travel Guide Spa Awards which was held in Melbourne, Australia. It was established in response to demand by the spa industry for a mission programme that was fair and transparent in stimulating the growth of the spa industry. The center was acknowledged for its varieties in treatment and products which includes reflexology massage, body massages, facials, couples’ massages and products such as Elemis. The firm was also recognized for its team of trained therapists who tailor perfect experiences and techniques which promote long-term health and wellbeing. The award recognizes organizations that drive up standards within the spa tourism and encourage a new era of growth. The wellness center has facilities inNairobi's Upper Hill, Muthaiga and Westlands.